          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Stop Super PAC-Candidate Coordination Act</b></p> <p>This bill defines "coordinated expenditures" with respect to federal elections, establishes that certain payments for coordinated expenditures are campaign contributions, and provides penalties for willfully violating limits related to making contributions to a candidate for coordinated expenditures. The bill also prohibits a candidate or federal office holder from soliciting, receiving, directing, or transferring funds to or on behalf of certain types of political committees. </p>]]></text>
